Mzansi A-listers such as Thembisa Mdoda, Minnie Dlamini-Jones and Nomuzi Mabena shimmered yesterday at the Sun Met at the Kenilworth Racecourse in Cape Town. Hosted by eight-time Olympic champion Usain Bolt and Dlamini-Jones for a second consecutive year, the horse-racing event is regarded as the first big event on the local celebrity social calendar. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD. TjiyaE@sundayworld.co.za